name: Tab Age Tracker v1.9
body:
This release focuses on stability improvements and bug fixes, particularly related to chart rendering and error handling.

### Improvements

- **Improved Error Handling**: Added comprehensive error handling throughout the extension to enhance stability
- **Enhanced CSP Support**: Updated content security policy for better compatibility with modern browsers
- **Null Element Protection**: Added null checks to prevent errors when DOM elements are not found
- **Chart.js Integration Fix**: Improved Chart.js integration to avoid rendering errors and display fallbacks
- **Service Worker Compatibility**: Fixed Service Worker (SW) issues for better background processing

### Bug Fixes

- Fixed potential errors in chart rendering when invalid data is present
- Improved handling of missing or invalid dates in tab data
- Added error recovery mechanisms to maintain app functionality even when errors occur
- Fixed issues with chart tooltips failing with invalid data
- Enhanced error messages for better debugging
